reviewText:
I think this the best if not one of the best movies Eleazar Garcia(Chelelo) he ever made. Too bad he didn't make too many like this. From the creative mind of Julian Garza "El Viejo Paulino", comes this real cool story packed with everything you could ask for. Drama, comic antics from Chelelo and Chis Chas, music and more. I highly reccomend it.

Una de las mejores peliculas de Chelelo. Lastima que no haya hecho mas peliculas asi. De la autoria de Julian Garza "El Viejo Paulino", esta pelicula tiene de todo. Drama, comedia, musica y mas. Se las recomiendo.
